    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require every secondary school to have multiple language options",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I would like the Government to require every secondary school to offer multiple languages. Many offer just French. This would allow students to choose from a selection of languages to learn. This country is very diverse and I believe every student should have the chance to learn new skills.",
